title: Deerhoof - Full Performance (Live on KEXP)
description:
http://KEXP.ORG presents Deerhoof performing live in the KEXP studio. Recorded May 3, 2023

Songs:
My Lovely Cat!
Scarcity Is Manufactured
Plant Thief
